{"tid":2381694,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"AOE2 DLC 已更新，兩個新文明...","createTime":"2021-01-26T19:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T05:54:57.000Z","uid":205394,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e97caf80bf1942f8ff7c49f4a1d5dc04155e9fa5","tid":2381694,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T19:56:31.000Z","msg":"大佬呀，唔好咁癲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次出新文明都搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西西里封建已經出到隻咁癲既兵<br />\n雙防3/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重識插塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封建無敵手，上到城堡時代都唔見得弱勢<br />\n<br />\n勃根地重有趣<br />\n城堡時代出重裝騎士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然無左品種<br />\n直接食物換金打到大後期都幾癲全民皆兵就真係唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係覺得呢兩個文明無做過平衡調整測就掉出黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343194c83d0e514dc169a7b14c43aac4713f7013","tid":2381694,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:56:37.000Z","msg":"城初有騎兵幾屈吓"},{"pid":"63142015c58333d56cc02c1c09414417698a371b","tid":2381694,"uid":18333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"封建冇3/3 wo, <br />\n仲要得5攻<br />\n佢升到城先自動加返攻防<br />\n封建60肉35金其實好貴， 初期戰鬥力弱過裝甲步兵<br />\n戰鬥力同村民好似差唔多<br />\n佢支塔又大， 成 2x2 ， 好多野都唔方便<br />\n<br />\n不過終於有正常討論技術post , 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}